## 2. Core LVS Protocol & Future Source Code  
The LVS Network protocol, reference node implementation, consensus algorithms, and system-level code **are NOT licensed under Apache 2.0** and are not open-sourced at this stage.

All protocol-level technology is protected under the **LVS Core Technology License**, which prohibits:

- redistribution  
- modification  
- commercial use  
- deployment  
- or publication of derivative works  

until the LVS Foundation releases the official open-source version.

This repository contains **documentation only**, not core protocol code.

Unauthorized publication or reverse-engineering of the LVS protocol is strictly prohibited.

